the best for black is to accept a slightly worse endgame with} Qc3 ({since} 
20... Qf6 {is too risky due to} 21. a5 {[%csl Rc6][%cal Ga5a6]} fxg3 (21...
Rhg8 22. a6 b6 23. N3d4 $1 {[%csl Rc6]} Nde5 24. Qa4 $1 {[%cal Gc1c5]} Ka8 25.
Rxc5 bxc5 26. Qb5 $40) 22. hxg3 h5 23. a6 b6 24. N3d4 $1 $40 {[%csl Rc6]}) 21.
Qxc3 bxc3 22. Rxc3 $14) 16. hxg3 h5 {Usually white react to black's h5 by
