Rxc6 {[%csl Rb8]} Ne5 29. Qc2 $1 Nfd7 30. Rc4 Nxc4 31. Rxd7 Qc5 32. Qe4 {[%cal
Gg2a8] A splendid game by the Asian champion. 1-0 Salem,A (2603)-Blomqvist,E 
