[%csl Ga5,Gc5] Solidifying the queenside.} (16... Ne6 17. Qe4 {is a
transposition to 15...Ne6}) (16... h5 $2 {does not work well with knight on c5.
} 17. b4 $40 {If this move comes with a tempo, it is a sign that something
must have gone wrong for black.} Ne6 18. b5 h4 19. bxc6 hxg3 20. Nb5 gxf2+ 21.
Rxf2 Qb6 22. Rb1 {1-0 Docx,S (2417)-Becker,M (2404)/Belgium 2012/EXT 2014}) 17.
Rfd1 {[%csl Ya5,Yc5,Ye5,Gf5,Rf7,Rf8,Rh7] In this line direct attempts with
