pieces.} 18. Rxd8+ Qxd8 19. Rd1 Qc7 20. Ne4 Bb4 21. Nf6 Rd8 22. f4 $1 {[%csl
Re5,Gf5] This is the difference between white and black knight. While Nf5 is
